<tree text="Saddabindu pakara&#x1E47;a&#x1E43;" target="text">
  <text>
    <centered>Namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa</centered>
    <hangnum nr="1"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Yassañeyyesu dhammesu, nāṇumattampaveditaṃ,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Natvāsaddhammasaṅghaṃtaṃ, saddabinduṃsamārabhe;</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="2"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Kādiritā navasaṅkhyā, kamenaṭā di yādica,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Pādayopañca saṅkhyātā, suññanāmā saraññanā;</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="3"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Sarehevasarāpubbe luttāvāvīpareramā,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Byañjanācāgamāvāvī dīgharassādisambhavā;</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="4"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Kākāsenāgatosisa keniddhimaccadassayi,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Arājakhvaggimesīnaṃ sotukammeghayitthiyo;</gatha>
    <centered>Iti sandhikappo samatto.</centered>
    <hangnum nr="5"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Buddhapumayuvasanta rājabrahmasakhācasā,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Yatādidehījantuca satthupitābhibhūvidū;</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="6"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Kaññāmmārattithipo, kkharaṇīnadirumātubhū,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Napuṃsaketiyantāca, padakammadadhāyuno;</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="7"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Gahitāgahaṇenettha suddhosyādyantakāpume,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Vimalāhontijāntehi thyaṃpañcantehidādhikā;</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="8"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Napuṃsakepayogātu janakāhontityantato,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Padhānānugatāsabba nāmasamāsataddhitā;</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="9"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Attiliṅgānipātādi tatoluttāvasyādayo,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Suttānurūpatosiddhā hontivattāmanādayo;</gatha>
    <centered>Iti nāmakappo samatto.</centered>
    <hangnum nr="10"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Chakārakesasāmismiṃ samāsohotisambhavā,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Taddhītākattukammasa, mpadānokāsasāmisu;</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="11"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Sādhattayamhiākhyāto kitakosattasādhane,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Sabbatthapaṭhamāvutte avuttedutiyādayo;</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="12"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Manasāmuninovutyā vanebuddhenavaṇṇite,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Vaṭṭāhitovivaṭṭatthaṃ bhikkhubhāvetibhāvanaṃ;</gatha>
    <centered>Iti kārakakappo samatto.</centered>
    <hangnum nr="13"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Rāsīdvipadikādvandā liṅgenavacanenaca,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Luttātulyādhikaraṇā bahubbīhītukhemarū;</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="14"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Tappurisācakhemorā dayācakammadhārayā,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Digavocāvyayāhārā etesabbepihāritā;</gatha>
    <centered>Iti samāsakappo samatto.</centered>
    <hangnum nr="15"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Kaccāditopiekamhā saddatoniyamaṃvinā,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Nekatthesatibhonteva sabbetaddhitapaccayā;</gatha>
    <centered>Iti taddhitakappo samatto.</centered>
    <hangnum nr="16"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Kattarināññathākamme tathābhāvetumerayā,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Sabbetepacadhātumhi saṅkhepenamarūmayā;</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="17"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Gamīmhātiguṇāphatto sambhavāaññadhātusu,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Anantāvapayogāte ādesapaccayādihi;</gatha>
    <centered>Iti ākhyātakappo samatto.</centered>
    <hangnum nr="18"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Kitādipaccayāsabbe, ekamhāapidhātuto,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Siyuṃnurūpatosatta, sādhanesatipāyato;</gatha>
    <centered>Iti kitakappo samatto.</centered>
    <hangnum nr="19"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Iminākiñcilesena, sakkāñātuṃjināgame,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Payogāñāṇināsindhu, rasovekenabindunā;</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="20"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Rammaṃsīghappavesāya, puraṃpiṭakasaññitaṃ,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Maggojumaggataṃmaggaṃ, saddāraññevisodhito;</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="21"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Teneva kiñci jalito jalito padīpo</gatha>
    <gatha type="2">Kaccāyanuttiratano citagabbhakoṇe,</gatha>
    <gatha type="3">Dhammādirājagurunā garumāmakena</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Dhammena yobbipatinā sagaruttanīto;</gatha>
    <centered>Iti saddabindu pakaraṇaṃ parisamattaṃ.</centered>
    <gatha type="1">Yosaññamo guṇadhano nayanaṃ nijaṃva</gatha>
    <gatha type="2">Sikkhāpayī mama mavaṃ sugatāgamādo,</gatha>
    <gatha type="3">Salloka puñja suhado padumādi rāma</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Nāmo mahā yativarā cariyo samayhaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="1">Saddhādhanena vasatā viditamhi pupphā</gatha>
    <gatha type="2">Rāmedhunā ariyavaṃsa dhajavhayena,</gatha>
    <gatha type="3">Santena ñāṇatilako tyaparākhyakena</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Bālānametamavidhīyi mayāhitāya;</gatha>
  </text>
